line_1: Will teach me a Game that he calls Lansquenet;
line_2: And the Captain, whose Kindness I ne'er can forget,

line_1: Captain CORMORANT won, when I learn'd Lansquenet;
line_2: A Sum, my dear Mother, far heavier yet,

line_1: Captain CORMORANT won, when I learn'd Lansquenet;
line_2: Two Hundred I paid him, and Five am in Debt.
